Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.connections.model

Author:
Donal Fellows
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BootReceiver
    A receiver of SpiNNaker boot messages.
    BootSender
    A sender of SpiNNaker Boot messages.
    Connection
    An abstract connection to the SpiNNaker board over some medium.
    EIEIOMessageHandler
    Handles a message received from an EIEIO connection.
    EIEIOReceiver
    A receiver of EIEIO data or commands.
    EIEIOSender
    A sender of EIEIO messages.
    Listenable<MessageType>
    How to listen for a message on a connection.
    MessageHandler<MessageType>
    Handles a message received from a connection.
    MessageReceiver<MessageType>
    A receiver of SpiNNaker messages.
    SCPReceiver
    Receives an SCP response from a socket.
    SCPSender
    A sender of SCP messages.
    SCPSenderReceiver
    Combo-interface.
    SDPReceiver
    A receiver of SDP messages.
    SDPSender
    A sender of SDP messages.
    SocketHolder
    Indicates a resource class that holds a network socket and that can answer basic questions about it.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidPacketException
    Indicates that a packet with an unsupported format was received.
